{"tid":333732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人記得細個第一段記憶？","createTime":"2017-07-24T05:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T01:37:28.000Z","uid":91451,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e788b2bf7e25759748541fca65fab0b1eab5bc4c","tid":333732,"uid":91451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"唔知點解我好記得自己細細個訓係床上野都未識講<br />\n阿哥沖奶粉比我飲結果熱得濟我倒到自己成面奶<br />\n我一直都認定呢個畫面係我人生第一段記憶<br />\n仲諗緊會唔會係熱得濟刺激到個腦<br />\n好似啪中左粒recording button咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人都有呢種第一段記憶？"},{"pid":"3a93adaf9fcc398b3fcc42fdb20217228aa3e2f7","tid":333732,"uid":110892,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:50:56.000Z","msg":"第一段記憶已經係幼稚園"},{"pid":"54070404847daeb9e66b777915233ae9ac2a2adf","tid":333732,"uid":53947,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:51:38.000Z","msg":"記得細個比人鬧<br />\n之係瀨屎"},{"pid":"780a31eb4ce289cc00250cddfc7a94e7053aa390","tid":333732,"uid":8175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:51:53.000Z","msg":"最早係第一日返幼稚園 喊到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9072075ae8f3d162f2b56deb1b2ba1da52af704d","tid":333732,"uid":91451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:52:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一段記憶已經係幼稚園</blockquote><br />\n有冇一段畫面係好肯定係人生第一次記得野？"},{"pid":"08dfc4d67eafb1519435e6a8dfa062ffd2b97284","tid":333732,"uid":73349,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:54:15.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會係聽完屋企人講再自己腦補出黎？"},{"pid":"e663966ff4751a2081f4e5f7db67966123567c33","tid":333732,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"幼稚園幼班 成班係走廊行 抬頭望住班高班係隔離行過"},{"pid":"146ff97e6cd189a9b642b160852ffccdb7986b5a","tid":333732,"uid":91451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實會唔會係聽完屋企人講再自己腦補出黎？</blockquote><br />\n有諗過 <br />\n但問過曬屋企人 冇人對件事有印象"},{"pid":"f8ee82501e325e6c708b4fc3a231d17811f7bef7","tid":333732,"uid":51478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:55:52.000Z","msg":"幼兒園插班個陣自我介紹 淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17df144e583aa6b183d9fcd7fcd0f697d9548e33","tid":333732,"uid":91451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幼稚園幼班 成班係走廊行 抬頭望住班高班係隔離行過</blockquote><br />\n細個差一年可以高好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38fbdaeffb3193cd976bc7c138f4beb78392dcb3","tid":333732,"uid":26937,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:57:10.000Z","msg":"發過一個夢<br />\n本身我係一舊石 <br />\n唔知點解會有靈魂然後撞左入而家呢個身體<br />\n跟住就醒左"},{"pid":"fc346575531a94622f30b32be3eb608a1b42d14b","tid":333732,"uid":49768,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:57:25.000Z","msg":"我連小學既野都唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最記得都係已經係中學既事"},{"pid":"47105332803f7ac1b9112960083985bb2a423e84","tid":333732,"uid":91451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發過一個夢<br />\n本身我係一舊石 <br />\n唔知點解會有靈魂然後撞左入而家呢個身體<br />\n跟住就醒左</blockquote><br />\n你意思呢個係人生第一個夢？"},{"pid":"e6e0430f96b49ce9d771812f96a0b995b8f90a13","tid":333732,"uid":80832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"細過發過既惡夢 到依家都記得"},{"pid":"e9e30b96bd475851b72cfd71caf8b362b2a577b9","tid":333732,"uid":91451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我連小學既野都唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最記得都係已經係中學既事</blockquote><br />\n我都有朋友話小三之前乜都唔記得<br />\n係真係雪白果隻 連睇番M記生日會相都冇印象 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c6f96d0ef4f9f565b00120b10d517cddac33f4","tid":333732,"uid":129453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:00:10.000Z","msg":"未必係第一段 啲時序已經搞唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過記得我同工人姐姐係廳度 媽咪行左入房 個廳個窗冇閂 個陣應該兩三歲咁<br />\n<br />\n工人姐姐就好似入左廚房整啲野咁 我就自己on99 laan左去窗台度企 仲攝攝左半個身出窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個陣係住緊28樓 已經係以前屋企最高個層黎<br />\n我仲要成個人打橫坐左係個窗度 唔記得係唔係冇窗花 定有窗花但我成個頭都攝得過出得個窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後就坐左係個窗度捉住個窗花當搖搖板咁鳩fing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n工人姐姐一出到黎見倒我坐左係個窗度就嚇到即刻入房叫我媽咪出黎<br />\n然後最後個畫面就係我媽咪好嬲咁望住我叫我落返黎 然後我就驚得濟落返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但唔係驚跌落去係驚比媽咪屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e2fe05a30d0f83c4dfa4612b092f01af0ad0a4","tid":333732,"uid":73349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:03:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實會唔會係聽完屋企人講再自己腦補出黎？</blockquote><br />\n有諗過 <br />\n但問過曬屋企人 冇人對件事有印象</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你點知係咪真係發生過呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我最早既記憶應該係拎住個波周圍跑，睇返啲相應該係兩歲既事，但唔肯定係我自己腦補定真係記得"},{"pid":"857686b2efcd66d6ed8fe34e4a0d52b697363ac8","tid":333732,"uid":91451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:06:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實會唔會係聽完屋企人講再自己腦補出黎？</blockquote><br />\n有諗過 <br />\n但問過曬屋企人 冇人對件事有印象</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你點知係咪真係發生過呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我最早既記憶應該係拎住個波周圍跑，睇返啲相應該係兩歲既事，但唔肯定係我自己腦補定真係記得</blockquote><br />\n其實我都冇辦法肯定<br />\n但就係有一種感覺 自從呢個畫面之後個腦就識記野"},{"pid":"20f9a9cce24819ec7c8fe8550269cac7460dc835","tid":333732,"uid":91451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:07:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未必係第一段 啲時序已經搞唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過記得我同工人姐姐係廳度 媽咪行左入房 個廳個窗冇閂 個陣應該兩三歲咁<br />\n<br />\n工人姐姐就好似入左廚房整啲野咁 我就自己on99 laan左去窗台度企 仲攝攝左半個身出窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個陣係住緊28樓 已經係以前屋企最高個層黎<br />\n我仲要成個人打橫坐左係個窗度 唔記得係唔係冇窗花 定有窗花但我成個頭都攝得過出得個窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後就坐左係個窗度捉住個窗花當搖搖板咁鳩fing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n工人姐姐一出到黎見倒我坐左係個窗度就嚇到即刻入房叫我媽咪出黎<br />\n然後最後個畫面就係我媽咪好嬲咁望住我叫我落返黎 然後我就驚得濟落返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但唔係驚跌落去係驚比媽咪屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你工人竟然唔係第一時間救你落黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0fce33c83e7d2e08f8a412160f4523ffc6ccd3","tid":333732,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一段記憶已經係幼稚園</blockquote><br />\n有冇一段畫面係好肯定係人生第一次記得野？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無, 點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092cf6b3a2bcb1d96bfbcac8db5d8d5fc3c2dfd0","tid":333732,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:47:01.000Z","msg":"幼稚園同學教我講仆街<br />\n之後我返屋企講 俾人打撚到仆街"},{"pid":"c703e1f9d442c759518aa38068de3b6fc4de1949","tid":333732,"uid":22376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幼稚園同學教我講仆街<br />\n之後我返屋企講 俾人打撚到仆街</blockquote><br />\n啱啱調轉 教人講仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c15fa988830d7c2055400087d22c85c0f1de6c3","tid":333732,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:57:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幼稚園同學教我講仆街<br />\n之後我返屋企講 俾人打撚到仆街</blockquote><br />\n啱啱調轉 教人講仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n相認?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddae382636798a56a4cc58d5db81e2c0a461604f","tid":333732,"uid":58484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:03:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a281a5679340798b6de343e4c4f7bf034e29984","tid":333732,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:07:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幼稚園同學教我講仆街<br />\n之後我返屋企講 俾人打撚到仆街</blockquote><br />\n啱啱調轉 教人講仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪就係你條仆街教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd6cd360bde389a5eb403d07c47b4041bd052f7","tid":333732,"uid":129453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:08:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>未必係第一段 啲時序已經搞唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過記得我同工人姐姐係廳度 媽咪行左入房 個廳個窗冇閂 個陣應該兩三歲咁<br />\n<br />\n工人姐姐就好似入左廚房整啲野咁 我就自己on99 laan左去窗台度企 仲攝攝左半個身出窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個陣係住緊28樓 已經係以前屋企最高個層黎<br />\n我仲要成個人打橫坐左係個窗度 唔記得係唔係冇窗花 定有窗花但我成個頭都攝得過出得個窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後就坐左係個窗度捉住個窗花當搖搖板咁鳩fing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n工人姐姐一出到黎見倒我坐左係個窗度就嚇到即刻入房叫我媽咪出黎<br />\n然後最後個畫面就係我媽咪好嬲咁望住我叫我落返黎 然後我就驚得濟落返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但唔係驚跌落去係驚比媽咪屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你工人竟然唔係第一時間救你落黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能佢驚佢過黎我會退後/唔聽佢講 我跌左落去既佢就仆街了 以前細個都曳 唔係好聽佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9d1689de221009c5370556b0c335e89c3b1081","tid":333732,"uid":85194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:36:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>未必係第一段 啲時序已經搞唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過記得我同工人姐姐係廳度 媽咪行左入房 個廳個窗冇閂 個陣應該兩三歲咁<br />\n<br />\n工人姐姐就好似入左廚房整啲野咁 我就自己on99 laan左去窗台度企 仲攝攝左半個身出窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個陣係住緊28樓 已經係以前屋企最高個層黎<br />\n我仲要成個人打橫坐左係個窗度 唔記得係唔係冇窗花 定有窗花但我成個頭都攝得過出得個窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後就坐左係個窗度捉住個窗花當搖搖板咁鳩fing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n工人姐姐一出到黎見倒我坐左係個窗度就嚇到即刻入房叫我媽咪出黎<br />\n然後最後個畫面就係我媽咪好嬲咁望住我叫我落返黎 然後我就驚得濟落返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但唔係驚跌落去係驚比媽咪屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你工人竟然唔係第一時間救你落黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能佢驚佢過黎我會退後/唔聽佢講 我跌左落去既佢就仆街了 以前細個都曳 唔係好聽佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我住一樓而且個頭大得濟穿唔過個窗花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f605ddfb659ae0e4d43644e0ee5020fbe4bf6589","tid":333732,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T18:14:06.000Z","msg":"兩歲幾第二日返幼稚園食茶點，屋企人無可能知，因為嗰日無家長<br />\n個記憶係第一身視點"},{"pid":"21cf15776cbd5c5f27bfcf6e6837c203a36505aa","tid":333732,"uid":6718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T01:02:05.000Z","msg":"剪小腸氣帶氧氣罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a55ecc6841aa9a27fccd63629ba251f9dcd6004","tid":333732,"uid":8583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:31:49.000Z","msg":"bb 果陣想飲水 但未識講野<br />\n淨係識 good啊 good啊 咁叫<br />\n全家人見我 係咁叫 good啊 good啊 好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我就一路叫good啊 一路係到喊<br />\n直到佢地比水我飲先停<br />\n<br />\n大過問番啊媽 都話記得有依段經歷<br />\n但唔知我係想飲水"},{"pid":"bbf13fff560868bba14bb2fd8fa9a92a5fff4f58","tid":333732,"uid":129453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:28:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>未必係第一段 啲時序已經搞唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過記得我同工人姐姐係廳度 媽咪行左入房 個廳個窗冇閂 個陣應該兩三歲咁<br />\n<br />\n工人姐姐就好似入左廚房整啲野咁 我就自己on99 laan左去窗台度企 仲攝攝左半個身出窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個陣係住緊28樓 已經係以前屋企最高個層黎<br />\n我仲要成個人打橫坐左係個窗度 唔記得係唔係冇窗花 定有窗花但我成個頭都攝得過出得個窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後就坐左係個窗度捉住個窗花當搖搖板咁鳩fing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n工人姐姐一出到黎見倒我坐左係個窗度就嚇到即刻入房叫我媽咪出黎<br />\n然後最後個畫面就係我媽咪好嬲咁望住我叫我落返黎 然後我就驚得濟落返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但唔係驚跌落去係驚比媽咪屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你工人竟然唔係第一時間救你落黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能佢驚佢過黎我會退後/唔聽佢講 我跌左落去既佢就仆街了 以前細個都曳 唔係好聽佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我住一樓而且個頭大得濟穿唔過個窗花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知個陣個腦諗緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54502a5115ae4029e679a8cc305e893d485255a","tid":333732,"uid":2926,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:42:19.000Z","msg":"我記得我同一大班人係條管道度慢慢爬上去，爬下爬無啦啦有一股熱流將我地推去一條好黑好黑嘅隧道，隧道入面得一點嘅光，跟住我地向住果點光博命游博命游，最後我第一個游入果點光之後我身邊嘅人就唔見哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c33dac01e50160fcfa8dbede91dedec3b316f5f","tid":333732,"uid":130339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:50:08.000Z","msg":"3歲去赤柱玩完夜晚發咗個惡夢<br />\n發夢自己喺美利樓然後火燭 好記得自己喊醒咗然後嗰晚發燒<br />\n唔知係咪第一段 但係段記憶好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85722693cd9d1d6b117e652528157b7cdbe02192","tid":333732,"uid":16915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:15:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩歲幾第二日返幼稚園食茶點，屋企人無可能知，因為嗰日無家長<br />\n個記憶係第一身視點</blockquote><br />\nSame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得係食通粉 好似係全世界最好食嘅野食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\